project description: 2d global blobs. This code produced results for the paper
"Radial convection of finite ion temperature, high amplitude plasma blobs"

The input.txt file is assumed unchanging by git with the command 
git update-index --assume-unchanged input.txt 
If you ever need to commit a change in input.txt use
git update-index --no-assume-unchanged input.txt

Problems: Invert class not used. 
          Diffusion on ln N and not N as in original 
